name: Governance Algo
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: gALGO is a wrapped version of ALGO that allows you to participate in Algorand Governance without losing your liquidity. Each gALGO can be burned for ALGO at the end of each governance period.
